Hellplague:
 
Hellplague stirred a while later, and sat up in the bed.  She needed some energon, and she did not know if there was any avalible on the ship.  She looked around in the room and found an insulated bin filled with small energon cubes.  Taking out two hand fulls, she stepped out and decided that Celeron needed reward for his work on the computer.  She heard someone in the back of the ship, and she stepped back there and found Celeron inspecting the engines.  She cleared her throat and handed Celeron a few cubes of energon.

rm2kmidi <kraftlos@...> wrote:
After a few hours, Celeron woke up.  The ship was rather quiet and he
decided now would be a good time to inspect the engines to see if he
could actually fix them.  He looked around for a light switch, then
began checking the condition of all the equipment in the engine hold. 
He figured this would take at least 2 hours....
